metadata.name: Devotion
metadata.description:
A touch to a spark  
Like a rose in bloom  
From the deepest womb  
This voyage left its mark  
 
This warmth ordained  
With a vibrant crown  
This desire named  
For our love abound  
 
My heart ached  
For your love  
What was missing  
Was my own  
Now its found  
My eyes open  
I see clearly  
To love is  
To invite freely  
To leave a  
Flower peacefully  
In the soil  
Breathing easily  
In the sun  
An expression of  
Natures love  
We are one
